Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来啦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.97,0:00:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么痛恨人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么身边\N偏偏带着人类的女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸跟邪见\N再加上小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎会发生什么大事件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.32,0:00:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.09,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.20,0:00:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.17,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.11,0:00:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.52,0:01:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.11,0:01:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.11,0:01:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找失踪的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不断朝着\N丑寅方向前进的这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也在寻找奈落的行踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第96话 邪见爷爷生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷\N小玲肚子快饿扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小玲去找东西吃  好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很烦耶  小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想这座森林\N会有东西给你吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.12,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点行不行…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找一下就回来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直不敢相信他竟然会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直不敢相信耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把所有的东西都吃光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连最后一包\N大蒜味薯条也吃光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃你一两包薯条\N干嘛那么小气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我特地留下来\N想要拿去送给地念儿的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种口味你不是一向不吃的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道随便尝两口\N就会吃得停不下来了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你说这下怎么办嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的地念儿是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们还记得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次云母\N不小心中了奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.83,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而治好它的消毒药\N就是地念儿给的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  是那个时候的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧这次\N会经过地念儿住的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想过去看看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道\N送人的礼物居然被偷吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么偷吃嘛真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这个地念儿也是个半妖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过他很善良\N而且待人很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和犬夜叉完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  既然送人的礼物吃光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆继续往前走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能拿到一些\N治疗瘴气的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以后着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是过去一趟比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次云母的事\N我也想去谢谢人家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家就一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于犬夜叉\N你想怎样随你便咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真是心胸狭窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个一定可以吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咿呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷果然厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷真的好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒虫最猛胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不马上给我滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光会留下一些没用的废物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近\N应该有最猛胜的巢穴才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我马上去找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个  毒虫的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔喔…嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲  快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一记  人头杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些缠人的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲  还不能把头抬起来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保护小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道等等\N杀生丸少爷会怎么夸我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是得救啦  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果追过去看看的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  帮我拔出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔出来没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气跟剧毒\N全都跑进我身体里面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子我死定了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道\N我可不是为了你才死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了杀生丸少爷才死的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道\N有什么办法可以解毒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着解毒了  小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟着杀生丸少爷这样到处游历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得自己好幸福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这次就这么死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这一生也算死而无憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我转告杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说我邪见会保佑他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上平安无事顺顺利利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得一定要转告他哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样看着邪见爷爷死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意帮你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说些话嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就拜托你看看咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷  你千万不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里一直向东走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会见到一个名叫\N“地念儿药草园”的药田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.98,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到那去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我采一些“千年草的果实”回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“千年草的果实”?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想救爷爷\N那就快去快回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太阳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳下山前  你还没有采到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“千年草的果实”回来救爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候\N最猛胜的剧毒会攻遍我全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一定会没命了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会在\N太阳下山之前赶回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会赶回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿吽  再快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这里吗  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我想应该是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉不是想怎样\N都随他便就可以了不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点小事还在意那么久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起嘛  我刚刚说得太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙老是这样\N连道歉都那么没诚意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.84,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股味道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落那些毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一些\N专门扑火找死的夏虫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别动手  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.79,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有感觉到\N四魂之玉碎片在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也感觉不到就在附近耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有感觉到那些奈落的傀儡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些毒虫说不定\N打算飞回奈落身边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别杀它们\N跟在后面看看再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说可以\N指引我们找到奈落吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  掉下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.05,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀…杀生丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只最猛胜是你杀的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是这只毒虫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是思考肤浅的家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找奈落的线索一断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后要找他简直难如登天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把话说在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这些毒虫自己突然死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢替自己狡辩\N你还是一样不要脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁喜欢帮自己狡辩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过实话实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛\N犬夜叉说的都是真话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你给我让开一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这小子多说无益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我的心情不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要动起手来\N可不会像之前那样手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大话最好少说两句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N你才不要哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们两个\N别打了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两兄弟还是一样感情不睦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿吽\N你在那边等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.55,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是药草园耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是个山姥妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.37,0:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.43,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想见一下地念儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们家地念儿\N谁都不想见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地念儿在家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想来拜托他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟他要点千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人中了剧毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到千年草果实救他\N他就要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里\N已经没有千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.89,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么躲在被子里不出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来不怕你见笑\N其实是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的地念儿是个半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有时候会像现在这样\N变成一个普通人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏这孩子胆子又特别小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他变成人类的时候\N根本不想让人看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不可以告诉我\N哪里可以采到千年草的果实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己可以去采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年草的果实\N是用来解妖怪剧毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…你是想要救妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是\N看上那个妖怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上妖怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是看上妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来你还不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事慢慢你一定会懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得当年我也跟你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆先别提这个啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.22,0:13:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很希望能救邪见爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉不觉得这个小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟戈薇姑娘很像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是那个姑娘呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是有那么点像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.47,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年草的果实\N就长在后山的山谷里头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里住着魑魅魍魉各种妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人类其实很难采得到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.11,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等天黑之后\N我就可以恢复正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一等\N天黑之后我陪你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我那些草长什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己爬上去采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟戈薇姑娘还真像耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.34,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…一个人\N孤零零的死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的  去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿吽  找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.23,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我觉悟吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸  我才不像你那么怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想要知道\N奈落的行踪对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落就在丑寅方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说奈落最后的形迹\N是往那边移动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑寅方向啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这条线索就容易多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这条命暂时寄放一下\N犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别走  杀生丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛要追奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  阿吽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了  就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿吽  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先帮我守着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去采千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈  哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.33,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的\N不希望再有其他人死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.34,0:18:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的\N不希望看见其他人死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.64,0:18:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷  不要死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.14,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望再有人死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒性开始发作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太阳就快下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.85,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玲是赶不及回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始觉得眼花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是幻觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀…杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.19,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见爷爷  你不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.22,0:20:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你说有个小姑娘\N来找过地念儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不晓得她是不是\N能平安的采到千年草的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真替她担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得她一定没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小姑娘\N跟戈薇姑娘很像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她跟戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.41,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那位小姑娘\N一定比我强得多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就像戈薇姑娘一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一颗温暖的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像太阳一样的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信等她长大之后\N一定也有一颗善良的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地念儿  你别再说了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  地念儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你恐怕对戈薇有些误解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇这个人\N很令人意外的小心眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.04,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了吧  地念儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说她心胸狭窄嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下  给我坐下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.22,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你终于醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  邪见爷爷\N你已经好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说\N连我…都一起死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.98,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷救了你\N还把你带回来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.78,0:21:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊  小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.42,0:21:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能再麻烦\N杀生丸少爷咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过邪见爷爷  还好你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊  小玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点放开我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.76,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.56,0:21:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑寅方向是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.94,0:21:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.04,0:21:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.35,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高兴\N大家又可以在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.62,0:22:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.73,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.17,0:22:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.11,0:22:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.86,0:22:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.40,0:22:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.13,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.38,0:23:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.01,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.62,0:23:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.13,0:23:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.76,0:23:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.96,0:23:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会只是出去散散步啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也没有什么特别的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.97,0:23:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是云母从来不会\N不说一声就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.00,0:23:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会出了什么事\N所以回不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.17,0:23:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到这一点\N我真的好担心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母该不会为了那件事\N离家出走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.71,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母为什么没回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.01,0:24:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你就这么不辞而别喔


